         <abstract>
            <p>Automatic meter reading and advanced metering infrastructure may be the future for data collection in the water sector, but implementation, especially for small utilities, can be a challenge. The benefits are proven, however, and new deployment approaches, cost reductions, and technological advances make these precision metering tools more accessible than ever.</p>
